## Title

The Architect of Worlds

## Visual Description

A humanoid figure stands at the center of a cosmic convergence surrounded by celestial bodies and unknown symbols.

The entity appears faceless, suggesting an intelligence beyond conventional identity.

Witness accounts describe feelings of memory distortion, impossible familiarity, and visions of worlds that never existed.

The artifact is believed to represent the origin of the Signal and the beginning of the Archive Era.

## Notable Inscriptions

- "The Archive Is Real. Reality Is Not."
- "We Do Not Find The Truth. The Truth Finds Us."
- "Do Not Trust Your Memory."

